Ranger Help for: ceremony
=========================

SYNTAX:      ceremony
USAGE:       Wilderness only
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     variable

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to perform a sacred ceremony to Gaia in the
wilderness. The ceremony strengthens the Ranger's connection to the
natural world and grants blessings that vary based on the terrain and
the Ranger's devotion. The SP cost depends on the type of ceremony
performed. This is a religious skill that can only be performed outside
of combat in wilderness terrain.
